Method Path Description <code>GET</code> <code>/api/serve/status</code> Modal app list for <code>agent-container-serve*</code> apps <code>POST</code> <code>/api/serve/deploy</code> Trigger a background <code>modal deploy</code> <p><code>POST /api/serve/deploy</code> body:</p> <pre><code>{
  "profile": "prod",
  "model":   "minimax-m2.5"
}
</code></pre> <p><code>model</code> is optional — only used when <code>profile</code> is <code>prod</code>. Omit it to use the default (<code>qwen3-coder</code>).</p>
